{"tid":1976924,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃色Youtube圈] YellopenRice第十四回 - 申子","createTime":"2020-04-17T14:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T09:38:09.000Z","uid":41818,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"072f8fe899f7fc46714ad77f3431a436fe563549","tid":1976924,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ixKNFq27jEQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FixKNFq27jEQ&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU983u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=e866167a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ixKNFq27jEQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇咗預告嘅觀眾就知今集《YellopenRice》介紹嘅「申子居酒屋」嘅兩位老闆都係「有故事的人」啦～其實除咗佢哋兩位有故事之外，呢間居酒屋都有其他故事講！聽講間餐叫「申子」係同「翻版陳浩南」Ian老闆去日本學廚嘅故事有關；亦都聽講佢哋係第一間公開招聘有案底手足嘅餐廳。究竟點解咁有勇氣成為第一間公開招有案底手足嘅餐廳？公開咗之後，又有冇俾黑警搞？A姐身為「黑警EX」，又表明立場經營黃店，又會唔會俾人特別針對？<br />\n<br />\n想知「黑警EX」x 「翻版陳浩南」經營嘅黃店仲有咩故仔？即刻收睇今集《YellopenRice》啦！"},{"pid":"7598e05dc0b2cadc644fad46f79070b6c53abc47","tid":1976924,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a588674c61c7012498b670fd617846dca021192","tid":1976924,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb381cbfe0a650f74e94994ad3c135d2cf1f264","tid":1976924,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:02:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2db8b27201d05fd7ddbe7f7786b6db5cc624586a","tid":1976924,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T01:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c255e59866b278ee9bd4480336003f8b5f54176","tid":1976924,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:40:48.000Z","msg":"申子"},{"pid":"39f597c06373605351be3